sqrt {K}}=3D{\sqrt {S}}+{\sqrt {T}},}"></span></dd></dl></dd></dl>
<dl><dd>where <i>K</i> is the area of the quadrilateral.<sup id=3D"cite_ref=
-FOOTNOTEJosefsson2013Thm._8_29-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://e=
