ps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trapezoid#cite_note-FOOTNOTEJosefsson2013Thm._15=
-30"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>30<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]<=
/span></a></sup></li>
<li>The angles in the quadrilateral <i>ABCD</i> satisfy <span class=3D"mwe-=
math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline=
 mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w=
3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle \sin A\sin C=3D\sin B\sin=
