<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Midsegment_and_height">Mids=
egment and height</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-edit=
section-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?ti=
